me99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1443\",\"downurlmash\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1443\",\"dwzdownurlmash\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1443\",\"gamename\":\"热血千刀斩（绯神兵高爆）\",\"excerpt\":\"《热血千刀斩》是一款经典复古传奇手游，散人追梦，超多装备！上线即送：自动回收！自动拾取！自动经验！自动货币！！超值装备！上百张地图精彩纷呈，等你来战！游戏中还有热血沙巴克活动，集齐你的兄弟一起血战！超多奖励等你拿！\",\"id\":1443,\"game_source\":\"\",\"device_type\":2,\"edition\":2,\"pic_xuanchuan\":\"\",\"strict\":0,\"userfc\":0,\"updatetime\":\"2025-10-04 08:00:00\",\"box_content\":\"1、上线即送：自动回收！自动拾取！自动经验！自动货币！！\\r\\n2、千骑踏羽渡青莲，魂绕天月问无极！\\r\\n3、沧海悠悠白沙暴，神州浩然神鬼怒！\\r\\n4、影夜默声逐七星，九炎辉狱弑穹天！\\r\\n5、赤霄红莲业都火，炽羽焚空绯蝶舞！\\r\\n6、风起沙城，斩龙求道，山海异界，傲视群雄！\",\"pic2\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250926/1bacca70053c5a2cb4882f9f7996bae7.jpg\",\"pic3\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250929/68da00dc58804.jpg\",\"pic4\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250929/68da015faee67.jpg\",\"cps_ratio\":0,\"hw_ratio\":0,\"hw_firstpay\":1,\"hw_otherpay\":1,\"firstpay\":1,\"otherpay\":1}');
INSERT INTO `gb_games` VALUES (239, 1, NULL, '寻龙英雄（1折免费版）', NULL, NULL, '冒险', 'discount', 'https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250930/68dba89c77807.png', 'https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250930/68dba8a38c850.jpg', '[\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250930/e0ec22d140a8fd7c4011d556b77a10db.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250930/30d7faa1225600944fc0b2fd827e261f.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250930/49a4cb63bc56096000eb20a052e9911f.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250930/6714e62404eca249aaaa6460c4acea13.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250930/6ad1413618f702c25933fd487e92af43.jpg\"]', 'https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13811.mp4', '游戏中玩家需要扮演一个来自九龙门派的初出茅庐的探险者，在同伴的帮助下寻访各个神秘诡异的古墓地宫，试图寻找一段被掩埋的历史，并解开许多年前针对九龙门派设下的阴谋。在冒险的过程中可以结识到不同属性的战斗伙伴，俊男美女一起联手战斗，战力也将随着提升。捕获宠物，驯服坐骑，一同开启炫酷的探险吧。\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1428', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1428', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1428', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1428', 'both', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', NULL, 0, 0.0, NULL, NULL, '2025-09-16 14:05:53', '0', '0', '0', 0, '1', '0', 'admin', '2025-12-26 08:42:41', '', '2025-12-26 09:49:14', '[导入源数据] {\"h5url\":\"\",\"h5\":0,\"welfare\":\"捕获宠物，驯服坐骑，一同开启炫酷的探险吧。\",\"interchangeable_role\":1,\"video\":\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13811.mp4\",\"text_cps\":\"\",\"new\":0,\"yuyue\":0,\"gametype\":\"冒险\",\"addtime\":\"2025-09-16 14:05:53\",\"gn_extension\":1,\"hw_extension\":1,\"cps_cpa\":\"CPS推广:60\",\"hw_cps_cpa\":\"CPS海外推广:40\",\"coupon_repeat\":\"\",\"pic1\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250930/68dba89c77807.png\",\"version\":0,\"c_version\":0,\"downurl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1428\",\"qrcode\":\"[base64已省略]\",\"weburl\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1428.html\",\"weburl_qr\":\"[base64已省略]\",\"dwzdo