INSERT INTO `gb_games` VALUES (319, 1, NULL, '封灵诀（0.05十倍返利免单版）', NULL, NULL, '角色扮演', 'discount', 'https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250924/68d3aededdf63.gif', 'https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250924/68d3aeecaf9cf.jpg', '[\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250730/23d5a38b377112e8879f9109324d5e29.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250730/2bf0541a51a655ed88509a461432f55f.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250730/08e8e297f61cbec8d4cf88222026c992.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250730/7220163a2c03e3a01f084d49055e3387.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250730/6d01c0bad62bf164051d05e736707e48.jpg\"]', 'https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13599.mp4', '天下大乱，游龙辈出。这原本是一个承平已久，青云圣教与普通凡人和谐相处的世界，但一场突如其来的阴谋颠覆了这一切。面对晦暗不明的局面，层出不穷的强大敌人、上古凶兽，你能否保持初心不断变强，一步步揭开导致天下大乱的真相，并成为天下第一的强者？', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1237', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1237', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1237', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1237', 'both', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', NULL, 0, 0.0, NULL, NULL, '2025-07-17 15:39:10', '0', '0', '0', 0, '1', '0', 'admin', '2025-12-26 08:42:42', '', '2025-12-26 09:49:14', '[导入源数据] {\"h5url\":\"\",\"h5\":0,\"welfare\":\"0.05折10倍返利，灵玉多到花不完！\",\"interchangeable_role\":1,\"video\":\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13599.mp4\",\"text_cps\":\"\",\"new\":0,\"yuyue\":0,\"gametype\":\"角色扮演\",\"addtime\":\"2025-07-17 15:39:10\",\"gn_extension\":1,\"hw_extension\":1,\"cps_cpa\":\"CPS推广:60\",\"hw_cps_cpa\":\"CPS海外推广:40\",\"coupon_repeat\":\"\",\"pic1\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250924/68d3aededdf63.gif\",\"version\":0,\"c_version\":0,\"downurl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1237\",\"qrcode\":\"[base64已省略]\",\"weburl\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1237.html\",\"weburl_qr\":\"[base64已省略]\",\"dwzdownurl\":\"https://qd.u