INSERT INTO `gb_games` VALUES (364, 1, NULL, '魔镜物语（0.1折每日千元代充）', NULL, NULL, '卡牌', 'discount', 'https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/740ea7dc3614ed9fcb88b5eb7b10dfbe.png', 'https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/2ce19e4d314455762971740218465e2c.jpg', '[\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/1593c5c10e0ad7945ce3ede44f235110.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/0d5b1531b5e7ba72923ac01a0634b95b.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/a85d200657688f0b7a839a9cb61acd38.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/5f68739b4c8a9d5b9f75354b21e6287e.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/5404cd0e44dcce1d4681bdaceebe6e39.jpg\"]', 'https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13341.mp4', '幻想破灭，光影交汇，无数童话人物深陷神秘梦境，堕入《魔镜物语》0.1折的世界中...纯洁的白雪公主逐渐黑化，而善良的矮人咯咯奸笑，熟知的角色全面颠覆，反转演绎经典剧情！「魔镜物语x卡皮巴拉」联动重磅登陆，卡皮巴拉能否在黑暗童话世界保持情绪稳定，敬请期待！游戏独有玩法全国同服公平竞技，踏入混沌斗技场，享受纯粹的策略对决！游戏福利迎来史诗级加强，首日即可直达VIP12！每日完成活跃就能领取千元代充卡，可购买礼包，等同真实付费！游戏免费赠送1000连抽，升级再得两万元充值卡，养成节奏全面加速！游戏版本持续更新中，更多创意玩法与强力伙伴陆续登陆童话世界！感受到魔镜的召唤了吗，梦境者，快来生成契约吧！', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005', 'both', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', NULL, 0, 0.0, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-27 16:12:00', '0', '0', '0', 0, '1', '0', 'admin', '2025-12-26 08:42:43', '', '2025-12-26 09:49:14', '[导入源数据] {\"h5url\":\"\",\"h5\":0,\"welfare\":\"全国同服竞技暗黑童话卡牌手游！\",\"interchangeable_role\":1,\"video\":\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13341.mp4\",\"text_cps\":\"\",\"new\":0,\"yuyue\":0,\"gametype\":\"卡牌\",\"addtime\":\"2025-04-27 16:12:00\",\"gn_extension\":1,\"hw_extension\":1,\"cps_cpa\":\"CPS推广:60\",\"hw_cps_cpa\":\"CPS海外推广:40\",\"coupon_repeat\":\"\",\"pic1\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/740ea7dc3614ed9fcb88b5eb7b10dfbe.png\",\"version\":0,\"