ame99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=411\",\"gamename\":\"一起来修仙（0.05折）\",\"excerpt\":\"《一起来修仙》是以修仙+山海经为背景的RPG策略回合制手游。游戏开创了独特的NPC交互系统，让玩家深入参与到故事流程之中，与不同的NPC进行交流，从每一段对话中拼凑出完整的大荒历史。\",\"id\":411,\"game_source\":\"\",\"device_type\":2,\"edition\":1,\"pic_xuanchuan\":\"\",\"strict\":0,\"userfc\":0,\"updatetime\":\"2024-12-26 10:00:00\",\"box_content\":\"福利介绍：\\r\\n1.充值0.05折\\r\\n2.上线送VIP3\\r\\n3.解锁战斗跳过\\r\\n4.赠10万灵石\\r\\n5.领百抽\\r\\n6.赠6480玄玉\",\"pic2\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241225/ea2cf8b144abc14fbf2841b862070366.jpg\",\"pic3\":\"\",\"pic4\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250729/688895af7d9b8.jpg\",\"cps_ratio\":0,\"hw_ratio\":0,\"hw_firstpay\":0.005,\"hw_otherpay\":0.005,\"firstpay\":0.005,\"otherpay\":0.005}');
INSERT INTO `gb_games` VALUES (407, 1, NULL, '魔法战线（0.1折趣味卡牌无限抽）', NULL, NULL, '经营', 'discount', 'https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/760966dedc5c8040f332d8c45a01f51d.gif', 'https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/021a8524094383d7d7461be0e0a392e6.jpg', '[\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/ec6403b28e2af36e22a15c987353ea69.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/a6786e6d3a72f7bd7b86e9c041732a96.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/ad171c4354fab462822a7f21a2dc0c1c.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/0e6d6a0d0d0e43fcfa6fe90464dd0efb.jpg\", \"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/ebeb4654e4bb1ae3952293efa688d2cb.jpg\"]', 'https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/12727.mp4', '《魔法战线》是一款集模拟经营、放置卡牌、开箱子及多种消消乐于一体的Q版手游0.1版本全民爽玩，开局就送神将孙悟空，每日再送100连抽和100把钥匙，豪华阵容任你搭配，开箱开到爽！\r\n三国、西游、封神等众多经典角色共同登场，爆笑超无厘头剧情，故事从一只猪妖讲起，不知从何而来，竟要抢夺三界食谱......你将从摆摊开始，收购酒楼、靠积累资源把酒楼做大做强，吸引更多客人从客人描述的故事获取美食线索，在冒险过程中获取食材和食谱，开发更多名菜，吸引奇人异士并和他们一起闯荡这个江湖！', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=449', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=449', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=449', 'https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=449', 'both', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', NULL, 0, 0.0, NULL, NULL, '2024-12-12 14:39:07', '0', '0', '0', 0, '1', '0', 'admin', '2025-12-26 08:42:43', '', '2025-12-26 09:49:14', '[导入源数据] {\"h5url\":\"\",\"h5\":0,\"welfare\":\"全新0.1折趣味卡牌，每日领取100连抽和100把钥匙，无限招募无限开箱！\",\"interchangeable_role\":1,\"video\":\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/12727.mp4\",\"text_cps\":\"\",\"new\":0,\"yuyue\":0,\"gametype\":\"经营\",\"addtime\":\"2024-12-12 14:39:07\",\"gn_extension\":1,\"hw_extension\":1,\"cps_cpa\":\"CPS推广:60\",\"hw_cps_cpa\":\"CPS海外推广:40\",\"coupon_repeat\":\"\",\"pic1\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20241218/760966dedc5c8040f332d8c45a01f51d.gif\",\"version\":0,\"c_version\":0,\"downurl\":\"https://qd.u