123&gid=1707\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1707\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1707\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\\"九界问仙（0.05折千元永久代金）\\\",\\\"excerpt\\\":\\\"开局仙魔供你选择，以无敌之姿镇压天骄，修道成仙，或斩尽世间枷锁，成就无上魔尊！全新仙侠手游《九界问仙》将满足你的幻想，你将扮演其中的修道者，寻找机缘，结识伙伴，揭开阴谋，应战强敌，在这仙侠世界中留下你浓重的一笔！\\\",\\\"id\\\":1707,\\\"game_source\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"device_type\\\":2,\\\"edition\\\":1,\\\"pic_xuanchuan\\\"', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":48}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:39', 72);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (907, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1676\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1676\",\"category\":\"卡牌\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251218/dba4bd2493b23334aaefc5a382135089.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:38\",\"description\":\"《超维计划》是一款融合了赛博朋克风格的卡牌策略手游。\\r\\n游戏以未来科技世界为背景，玩家通过收集和培养独特的赛博伙伴，组建强大的阵容参与战斗。\\r\\n每个伙伴都拥有独特的技能和属性，玩家需要灵活搭配阵容，在精美的赛博朋克画风下，体验紧张刺激的卡牌对决。\\r\\n除了丰富的剧情主线外，大量成长系统和趣味的活动玩法也等待着玩家的探索。\\r\\n还在苦恼找不到志同道合的游戏伙伴?《超维计划》社交舞台已搭建!这是一款融合赛博朋克与卡牌策略的爆款手游。和好友一起组建赛博伙伴战队，在炫酷的赛博城市背景下，运用策略搭配技能，横扫卡牌战场。游戏内实时交流，随时分享战术心得。每周更新的限时副本、特色活动更是社交互动的绝佳契机。首发曝光中，拉上你的小伙伴，一起在超维世界开启社交冒险之旅，让友情在战斗中升温!\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1676\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251218/6d794db4a0eb7e7aed1048ebae679d45.png\",\"id\":51,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1676\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"1\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-12-03 11:01:39\",\"name\":\"超维计划（0.1折GM免费版）\",\"params\":{},\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"0.1折赛博风放置卡牌千抽福利\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/14076.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"new\\\":1,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"卡牌\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-12-03 11:01:39\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251218/6d794db4a0eb7e7aed1048ebae679d45.png\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1676\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1676.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1676\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1676\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":51}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:39', 87);
