23&gid=1643\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1643\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1643\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\\"一念剑歌（变态高爆）\\\",\\\"excerpt\\\":\\\"踏入这个如诗如画的修仙世界，您将亲身体验渡劫飞升的紧张刺激、驾驭飞剑的自由畅快、召唤法宝的无穷力量以及与仙灵并肩作战的深厚友情。更有海量PVE内容等待挑战，一切精彩，尽在《一念剑歌》，即刻启程，开启您的修仙之旅！\\\",\\\"id\\\":1643,\\\"game_source\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"device_type\\\":2,\\\"edition\\\":1,\\\"pic_xuanchuan\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":122}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:40', 77);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (982, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1641\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1641\",\"category\":\"卡牌\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251127/0c4bdfcd919b47c9e78c016909f2da0f.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:39\",\"description\":\"《少年西游记2（免费版）》是一款国潮朋克卡牌RPG手游,讲述了平行时空的大唐，人们发现了超级能源的“灵衍”。然而灵衍的过度使用促生了魔衍，在其影响之下万物皆有可能陷入癫狂，看似繁华的世界已经摇摇欲坠。作为一名不受魔衍影响的灵衍师，玩家可与来自三界不同阵营的衍灵一起，踏上西行求法之路，拯救逐步走向失控的世界\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1641\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251127/8df7efd053c1d99f437638945830a5f3.png\",\"id\":121,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1641\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-11-25 09:05:23\",\"name\":\"少年西游记2（免费版）\",\"params\":{},\"promotionDesc\":\"禁海外推广\",\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"《少年西游记2（免费版）》是一款国潮朋克卡牌RPG手游。\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/14039.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"禁海外推广\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"卡牌\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-11-25 09:05:23\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251127/8df7efd053c1d99f437638945830a5f3.png\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1641\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg