/qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1570\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1570\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1570\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\\"合金风暴（0.1折开局领千抽）\\\",\\\"excerpt\\\":\\\"以SNK经典格斗游戏《拳皇》为蓝本，化身格斗导师招募草薙京、八神庵、不知火舞，集结三神器队、音巢组织、大蛇一族等传奇势力，组建最强战队征战KOF大赛！从初赛舞台启程，挑战极限流道场，血战音巢基地&大蛇封印，最终登顶格斗之巅，探寻拳皇终极奥义！\\\",\\\"id\\\":1570,\\\"game_source\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"de', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":169}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:41', 54);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (1028, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1554\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1554\",\"category\":\"卡牌\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251114/23037b1b7625f2cdef8be9eef3af7bd0.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:40\",\"description\":\"\\\"《魂之追梦》——当诸神相遇，谁主沉浮？\\r\\n在命运之树的庇护下，一座横跨东西的神殿之城巍然耸立。\\r\\n这里是奥林匹斯山的余晖与东方仙侠的云海交汇之地，是北欧战神与华夏猛将并肩作战的战场，踏上征服诸神之阶的荣耀之路！\\r\\n《魂之追梦》是一款融合西方神话史诗与东方传奇英雄的策略卡牌手游，带你穿越时空，集结亚瑟、奥丁、雷神托尔、孙悟空、吕布、宫本武藏等百位神魔英灵，开启一场跨越文明的终极之战！\\r\\n恢弘世界观：从北欧诸神到希腊众神，从埃及法老到凯尔特精灵，数百位神话英雄集结于此，等待你召唤觉醒。\\r\\n唯美画风：精致卡牌立绘，每一帧都宛如一幅神话画卷。\\r\\n海量英雄卡牌：UR、SSR、SR等稀有卡牌，通过“心愿召唤”、“幸运转盘”、“限时活动”获取，打造属于你的神之战队。\\r\\n自由搭配阵容：元素相克、技能联动、羁绊加成，策略深度拉满，每一场战斗都是智慧的较量！\\\"\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1554\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251114/e6af0217af44c4fdb7f80df5496805c5.png\",\"id\":170,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1554\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-11-03 14:17:10\",\"name\":\"魂之追梦（0.1折）\",\"params\":{},\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"《魂之追梦》——当诸神相遇，谁主沉浮？\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13941.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"卡牌\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-11-03 14:17:10\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:0\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:30\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251114/e6af0217af44c4fdb7f80df5496805c5.png\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1554\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1554.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1554\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1554\\\",\\\"dwzd', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":170}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:41', 65);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (1029, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1568\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1568\",\"category\":\"卡牌\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251114/3aa4cc1c09334be76a2263a3f9d39856.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:40\",\"description\":\"踏入《艾尔指挥官》的世界，一场惊心动魄的斩鬼冒险就此展开！\\r\\n在这里，你将化身鬼杀队的英勇战士，与灶门炭治郎、祢豆子等熟悉的角色并肩作战。运用水之呼吸、炎之呼吸等华丽且强大的技能，在刀光剑影中与恶鬼展开殊死搏斗。\\r\\n游戏完美复刻动漫经典场景，阴森的鬼屋、静谧的森林，每一处细节都栩栩如生，让你身临其境。紧张刺激的战斗节奏，拳拳到肉的打击感，给你带来前所未有的游戏体验。\\r\\n无论是单人挑战关卡，突破自我极限，还是与好友组队开黑，共同对抗强大的鬼王，都能让你感受到热血与激情。\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1568\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251114/546e6cdf2b78c9d5696f5a96cfbf831d.gif\",\"id\":171,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1568\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-11-05 10:48:47\",\"name\":\"艾尔指挥官（0.1折决战无限城）\",\"params\":{},\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"踏入《艾尔指挥官》的世界，一场惊心动魄的斩鬼冒险就此展开！\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13957.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"卡牌\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-11-05 10:48:47\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251114/546e6cdf2b78c9d5696f5a96cfbf831d.gif\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1568\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1568.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1568\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1568\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1568\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\\"艾尔指挥官（0.1折决战无限城）\\\",\\\"excerpt\\\":\\\"踏入《艾尔指挥官》', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":171}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:41', 69);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (1030, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1575\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1575\",\"category\":\"卡牌\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20251113/6915a3d69110b.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:40\",\"description\":\"丧尸病毒正在全球蔓延！\\r\\n人类最大的堡垒城市Z城已遭入侵！您将统领不断壮大的军队征服此城，成为真正的领导者。同时必须在这崩坏的世界中学会生存之道。\\r\\n成为抵抗入侵的领袖\\r\\n在这片混乱中，您已将Z城设为根据地。高墙用以抵御尸群，保护墙内民众——他们是幸存者最后的希望。\\r\\n招募英雄增强实力\\r\\n入侵永无止境，尸潮将愈发凶猛。是时候招募更多英雄组建超凡战队，每位成员都拥有独特个性与能力。\\r\\n探索剧情收集物资\\r\\n生存需要人口、装备、补给和武器。探索未知领域获取资源，扩大要塞与势力范围。\\r\\n守护珍视之人\\r\\n作为指挥官，保护心爱的佳人是您的职责。与她们约会并提供安全庇护，记住她们既是人类最后的希望，也是这黑暗世界中的光芒。\\r\\n创建战盟协同作战\\r\\n您可与伙伴建立可靠战盟，通过谈判、战斗甚至背叛击溃敌人！与人性的博弈相比，屠杀丧尸不过是儿戏。\\r\\n处理政务重建家园\\r\\n建造发电厂与军火库、处理市政事务、强化城防巡逻、清理死亡公路、举办庆典...更重要的是携手重建家园，带领民众走向光明未来。\",\"deviceSupport\":\"android\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1575\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20251113/6915a3cc1a8c9.png\",\"id\":172,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1575\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-11-07 09:28:58\",\"name\":\"2047（0.1折天天送648）\",\"params\":{},\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"末日重生，0.1折爽刷尸潮爆神装！天天送代金券！\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13965.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"卡牌\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-11-07 09:28:58\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20251113/6915a3cc1a8c9.png\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1575\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1575.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1575\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":172}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:41', 69);
