me99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1453\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1453\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1453\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\\"女神幻想（0.1折送5星英雄）\\\",\\\"excerpt\\\":\\\"这是一个绮丽与幻想交织的世界！数百位女神化身卡牌，等待你的召唤。通过策略组合与羁绊养成，解锁专属剧情与华丽战斗特效，在冒险中唤醒她们沉睡的力量！与心仪女神并肩作战，书写属于你的次元传奇！“队长，听到.....我的心跳了吗？”\\\",\\\"id\\\":1453,\\\"game_source\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"device_type\\\":2,\\\"e', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":246}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:42', 45);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (1105, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1397\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1397\",\"category\":\"角色扮演\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250923/68d24153633ed.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:41\",\"description\":\"《黑月（0.1折每日送现金）》是一款横版格斗手游，游戏讲述了黑月再次降临，主角们共同抵抗黑月入侵的故事。在命运的安排下，成为黑月学院主角团一员的你，肩负起了守护人类世界和平的重任。揭秘黑月降临的阴谋，探寻魔女消失的记忆，一场关乎世界存亡的冒险之旅即将展开。黑月元年，世界上空有大量黑粒子汇聚，汇聚成一轮黑月，世界突然与另一个平行时空发生了耦合，无数来自高维异种生物杀戮机器从『黑月』入侵，人类经过数十年惨烈的抗争，终于以巨大的牺牲封印了『黑月』，换来了人类和平的喘息时机！\\r\\n然而，没有消失的黑月死门，像高悬的达摩克利斯之剑，让人类在末日的威胁下暗流涌动挣扎着寻求不同的出路。而你，作为降临世界的『命运之子』，又将把世界的未来推向何方？\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1397\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250919/68cd1a2c7c6e7.png\",\"id\":247,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1397\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-09-05 13:52:49\",\"name\":\"黑月（0.1折每日送现金）\",\"params\":{},\"promotionDesc\":\"禁海外推广\",\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"指尖华尔兹，超燃DIY横版格斗手游\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13777.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"禁海外推广\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"角色扮演\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-09-05 13:52:49\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250919/68cd1a2c7c6e7.png\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1397\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1397.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1397\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1397\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1397\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\\"', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":247}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:42', 63);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (1106, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1392\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1392\",\"category\":\"策略\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20251210/79ffe62e3d537135fea194c4c3e5f44b.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:41\",\"description\":\"岁月如梭，烽烟未息！十年前，我们并肩征战沙场，在战国七雄的版图上挥斥方遒，十年后，《天子令（七雄争霸正版0.1折）》手游承载万亿玩家的青春记忆，以 ​​「经典重铸版」​​ 之姿邀您再续战国史诗！现版本全场物价0.1折，首充仅需0.01元！更有海量充值卡赠予，助您七国争雄！游戏内将中原地区分为燕、韩、赵、魏、齐、楚、秦七大国，玩家可在本国地图内迁移城池、建立联盟，在国战中互相反复争夺。不同国家的玩家也可以集体远征攻打其他国家。我们在延续经典的千重楼、钓鱼等玩法的同时，更有实时国战、跨服远征、联盟战场、逐鹿中原。游戏内有多兵种进行搭配及克制，感受克敌制胜，以少胜多的胜利快感。玩家通过发展自己的城池，增加势力范围，培养独当一面的无敌武将，不断壮大实力，与朋友建立联盟，架设丝绸之路，高筑墙，广积粮，招兵买马，称霸全国，问鼎天下！战国烽火因您重燃，这杯十年的酒，敬永不落幕的争霸之心！\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1392\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250928/68d9058b7550e.gif\",\"id\":249,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1392\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-09-04 09:32:53\",\"name\":\"天子令（七雄争霸正版0.1折）\",\"params\":{},\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"七雄争霸正版0.1折！\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13772.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"策略\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-09-04 09:32:53\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/data/upload/game/20250928/68d9058b7550e.gif\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1392\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1392.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1392\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1392\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.c', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":249}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:42', 72);
