ag=GMS123&gid=955\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=955\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=955\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\\"迷你勇士（0.1折口袋妖怪觉醒）\\\",\\\"excerpt\\\":\\\"《迷你勇士（0.1折口袋妖怪觉醒）》 是一款卡牌养成游戏，熟悉的精灵带你回到童年重温经典剧情，收集心仪的小精灵，通过探以太乐园、时空裂隙、对战工厂等特色玩法收集资源养成小精灵，在这个充满魔幻的世界里，探索无限可能！\\\",\\\"id\\\":955,\\\"game_source\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"device_type\\\":2,\\\"edition\\\":1,\\\"pic_xuanchuan\\\":\\\"', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":361}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:43', 78);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (1222, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005\",\"category\":\"卡牌\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/2ce19e4d314455762971740218465e2c.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:42\",\"description\":\"幻想破灭，光影交汇，无数童话人物深陷神秘梦境，堕入《魔镜物语》0.1折的世界中...纯洁的白雪公主逐渐黑化，而善良的矮人咯咯奸笑，熟知的角色全面颠覆，反转演绎经典剧情！「魔镜物语x卡皮巴拉」联动重磅登陆，卡皮巴拉能否在黑暗童话世界保持情绪稳定，敬请期待！游戏独有玩法全国同服公平竞技，踏入混沌斗技场，享受纯粹的策略对决！游戏福利迎来史诗级加强，首日即可直达VIP12！每日完成活跃就能领取千元代充卡，可购买礼包，等同真实付费！游戏免费赠送1000连抽，升级再得两万元充值卡，养成节奏全面加速！游戏版本持续更新中，更多创意玩法与强力伙伴陆续登陆童话世界！感受到魔镜的召唤了吗，梦境者，快来生成契约吧！\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/740ea7dc3614ed9fcb88b5eb7b10dfbe.png\",\"id\":364,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-04-27 16:12:00\",\"name\":\"魔镜物语（0.1折每日千元代充）\",\"params\":{},\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"全国同服竞技暗黑童话卡牌手游！\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13341.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"卡牌\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-04-27 16:12:00\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250507/740ea7dc3614ed9fcb88b5eb7b10dfbe.png\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/1005.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=1005\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1005\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=1005\\\",\\\"gamename\\\":\\', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":364}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:43', 47);
INSERT INTO `sys_oper_log` VALUES (1223, '游戏管理', 1, 'com.ruoyi.web.controller.gamebox.GbGameController.add()', 'POST', 1, 'admin', '研发部门', '/gamebox/game', '127.0.0.1', '内网IP', '{\"androidUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=850\",\"apkUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=850\",\"category\":\"放置\",\"coverUrl\":\"https://cp.u2game99.com/storage/operator/20250425/2cd68dd26951ce4b11ef2ce3eebe3014.jpg\",\"createBy\":\"admin\",\"createTime\":\"2025-12-26 08:42:42\",\"description\":\"为了争夺上古世界的统治，无数神魔在无尽岁月的争斗中陨落，最终形成了主宰世界的六大阵营。\\r\\n然而，跨越万载的和平下，是黑暗势力不断滋长的野心。战火重燃，有志之士纷涌而起，谁能为世界再次带来和平？\\r\\n\\r\\n【游戏特色】\\r\\n·放置战斗，挂机变强\\r\\n点开战斗便无需关注战场，自由切换至其他场景，护肝护眼，轻松闯关！\\r\\n挂机也能获得奖励，你的英雄们将一直为你自动战斗，一觉睡醒就能变强！\\r\\n\\r\\n·告别羁绊，阵容随心\\r\\n去除一般卡牌游戏的羁绊系统，仅保留六大阵营的克制关系，彻底释放英雄，让阵容搭配更加随心所欲！\\r\\n\\r\\n·良心抽卡，十连必金\\r\\n不需要苦苦攒保底，十连召唤必得五星金卡，卡池无锁定，五星无废卡！\\r\\n\\r\\n·无损回退，自由养成\\r\\n已经培养的英雄，可以通过回退返还所有消耗的材料和英雄，妈妈再也不用担心我养错英雄了！\\r\\n\\r\\n·真实画风，享受旅途\\r\\n对二次元已经审美疲劳？壮丽唯美的景色，精致真实的人物，带你领略别样的异世界之旅！\",\"deviceSupport\":\"both\",\"downloadCount\":0,\"downloadUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=850\",\"gameType\":\"discount\",\"hasLowDeductCoupon\":\"0\",\"hasSupport\":\"0\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://p1.277sy.com/2025/04/22/680712e874f7c.png\",\"id\":365,\"iosUrl\":\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=850\",\"isHot\":\"0\",\"isNew\":\"0\",\"isRecommend\":\"0\",\"launchTime\":\"2025-03-20 15:14:37\",\"name\":\"上古纷争（0.1折免费版）\",\"params\":{},\"remark\":\"[导入源数据] {\\\"h5url\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"h5\\\":0,\\\"welfare\\\":\\\"神魔放置，登录送百抽，0.1折送6480代金劵\\\",\\\"interchangeable_role\\\":1,\\\"video\\\":\\\"https://mp4.277sy.com/sp/13165.mp4\\\",\\\"text_cps\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"new\\\":0,\\\"yuyue\\\":0,\\\"gametype\\\":\\\"放置\\\",\\\"addtime\\\":\\\"2025-03-20 15:14:37\\\",\\\"gn_extension\\\":1,\\\"hw_extension\\\":1,\\\"cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS推广:60\\\",\\\"hw_cps_cpa\\\":\\\"CPS海外推广:40\\\",\\\"coupon_repeat\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"pic1\\\":\\\"https://p1.277sy.com/2025/04/22/680712e874f7c.png\\\",\\\"version\\\":0,\\\"c_version\\\":0,\\\"downurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=850\\\",\\\"qrcode\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"weburl\\\":\\\"https://www.u2game99.com/wg/1037/850.html\\\",\\\"weburl_qr\\\":\\\"[base64已省略]\\\",\\\"dwzdownurl\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?ag=GMS123&gid=850\\\",\\\"downurlmash\\\":\\\"https://qd.u2game99.com/down.html?mash=TbZIVBOR&gid=850\\\",\\\"dwzdownurlmash\\\":\\\"ht', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200,\"data\":365}', 0, NULL, '2025-12-26 08:42:43', 40);
